All background images should be scaled to 1920x1080

*Backgrounds can be updated more than once.*


To add your Ziggurat:
- First download the original image from IPFS
- Then remove the background color leaving a transparent background
(use photoshop etc) and save as transparent PNG (3000x3000).

*Ziggurat cannot be updated more than once. F5 to refresh.*
